{"tid":1645973,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大陸國台辦指責蔡英文雙十講話污蔑攻擊「一國兩制」","createTime":"2019-10-11T05:59:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T08:36:18.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"21d722821a6205241137a87c77cb08de0987fee1","tid":1645973,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T05:59:18.000Z","msg":"台灣的蔡英文總統在雙十發表講話，大陸國台辦回應時指責充斥著對抗思維和敵對意識。<br />\n<br />\n國台辦發言人馬曉光表示，講話企圖借污蔑攻擊「一國兩制」，製造仇視大陸的氛圍，壓制台灣民眾希望發展經濟、改善民生、緩和兩岸關係的主流民意，謀取選舉利益。<br />\n<br />\n馬曉光又形容講話顛倒黑白，暴露民進黨當局製造兩岸對立衝突、破壞台海和平穩定、悖逆島內求安望治主流民意，以及兩岸與中華民族整體利益，強調搞對抗沒有出路，謀「台獨」更是絕路，「台獨」是對廣大台灣同胞的嚴重威脅。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%B0%E8%BE%A6%E6%8C%87%E8%B2%AC%E8%94%A1%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E9%9B%99%E5%8D%81%E8%AC%9B%E8%A9%B1%E6%B1%A1%E8%94%91%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A-%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A9%E5%88%B6-045217550.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2599%25B8%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258F%25B0%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E8%2594%25A1%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%2596%2587%25E9%259B%2599%25E5%258D%2581%25E8%25AC%259B%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E6%25B1%25A1%25E8%2594%2591%25E6%2594%25BB%25E6%2593%258A-%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2588%25B6-045217550.html&d=tgdX0zC4r3YoKKw%2Bq%2FbDqWLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=fdc52d91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%B0%E8%BE%A6%E6%8C%87%E8%B2%AC%E8%94%A1%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E9%9B%99%E5%8D%81%E8%AC%9B%E8%A9%B1%E6%B1%A1%E8%94%91%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A-%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A9%E5%88%B6-045217550.html</a>"},{"pid":"88395682a5f8800e3bad7bc7de5dcf3260714bdb","tid":1645973,"uid":176282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T06:01:18.000Z","msg":"耿爽：我不爽"},{"pid":"71c4dd3003218ab78a9d57df3c4ceb633a6c44d7","tid":1645973,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88395682a5f8800e3bad7bc7de5dcf3260714bdb","tid":1645973,"uid":176282,"like":0,